This repo is **pierce-connaughton-portfolio-react** — a Vite + React + TypeScript portfolio SPA (MUI, SCSS modules). No test suite, no monorepo, no Azure DevOps.

**Start here:** [`.agents/README.md`](../../.agents/README.md)

| Task | Read |
|------|------|
| Multi-step or coordinated work | [`.agents/roles/orchestrator.md`](../../.agents/roles/orchestrator.md) |
| Implement changes | [`.agents/roles/coder.md`](../../.agents/roles/coder.md) |
| File layout & conventions | [`.agents/standards/project.md`](../../.agents/standards/project.md) |
| Ambiguous requests | [`.agents/workflows/ask-when-unclear.md`](../../.agents/workflows/ask-when-unclear.md) |

Quality gates: `npm run lint` and `npm run build`. Verify UI with `npm run dev` when needed.

Commit only when the user explicitly asks.
